{"ja391:0.1":"Jataka ","ja391:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","ja391:0.3":"Kharaputtavagga ","ja391:0.4":"6. Vijjadharajataka ","ja391:1.1":"“Dubbannarupam tuvamariyavanni, ","ja391:1.2":"Purakkhatva panjaliko namassasi; ","ja391:1.3":"Seyyo nu te so udava sarikkho, ","ja391:1.4":"Namam parassattano capi bruhi”. ","ja391:2.1":"“Na namagottam ganhanti raja, ","ja391:2.2":"Sammaggatanujjugatana deva; ","ja391:2.3":"Ahanca te namadheyyam vadami, ","ja391:2.4":"Sakkohamasmi tidasanamindo”. ","ja391:3.1":"“Yo disva bhikkhum caranupapannam, ","ja391:3.2":"Purakkhatva panjaliko namassati; ","ja391:3.3":"Pucchami tam devarajetamattham, ","ja391:3.4":"Ito cuto kim labhate sukham so”. ","ja391:4.1":"“Yo disva bhikkhum caranupapannam, ","ja391:4.2":"Purakkhatva panjaliko namassati; ","ja391:4.3":"Dittheva dhamme labhate pasamsam, ","ja391:4.4":"Sagganca so yati sarirabheda”. ","ja391:5.1":"“Lakkhi vata me udapadi ajja, ","ja391:5.2":"Yam vasavam bhutapatiddasama; ","ja391:5.3":"Bhikkhunca disvana tuvanca sakka, ","ja391:5.4":"Kahami punnani anappakani”. ","ja391:6.1":"“Addha have sevitabba sapanna, ","ja391:6.2":"Bahussuta ye bahuthanacintino; ","ja391:6.3":"Bhikkhunca disvana mamanca raja, ","ja391:6.4":"Karohi punnani anappakani”. ","ja391:7.1":"“Akkodhano niccapasannacitto, ","ja391:7.2":"Sabbatithiyacayogo bhavitva; ","ja391:7.3":"Nihacca manam abhivadayissam, ","ja391:7.4":"Sutvana devinda subhasitani”ti. ","ja391:8.1":"Vijjadharajatakam chattham. "}